Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:35.12,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1360,558)}Episode 8: Inherited Will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.53,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Slime-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.59,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:43.69,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.83,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,killed someone I cared about again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:51.74,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,With my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.14,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Slime-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.10,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:11.93,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I want people to remember my \Nstory... and know that I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:22.20,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So Shizu-san told me what happened, \Nthough her recollection was vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.98,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,She spoke of how Ifrit possessed \Nher after she was summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:30.34,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and how she ended up killing her friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.57,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.16,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,After Pirino died,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:42.19,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to serve the \NDemon Lord as his closest aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.07,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But then I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:47.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Met who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.68,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.18,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.72,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... The Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.64,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,There was a battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.88,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,and the Demon Lord abandoned his castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.67,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,leaving me behind as the rear guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:10.17,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the will of the fire spirit Ifrit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.18,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,or was it of my own volition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.48,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.21,Flashback,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't beat her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.82,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.62,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't suppose it was the same \None who sealed Veldora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:47.22,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be killed instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.46,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But then she spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.77,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me why I was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.07,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,how I had stayed alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:03.89,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I was a majin, and she \Nbelieved everything I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.57,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,She told me, "It's all right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.59,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,My emotions came back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.43,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Hero took me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:22.47,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who gave me that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.87,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,She said it would boost my magic resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.70,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,and help suppress Ifrit, \Nthe spirit dwelling within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.64,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.64,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,By traveling with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:45.99,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I learned about this world, \Nand I learned magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:53.15,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Through the power of the mask, I even \Nlearned to use Ifrit's power, to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.93,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,By helping others, and fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.88,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you came to be known \Nas the Conqueror of Flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was an awesome attack, \Nall right! You were on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:15.96,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy traveling with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.24,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.26,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.53,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then she disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.91,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.18,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:33.84,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.40,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.75,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm certain we'll meet again."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.26,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.80,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.43,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to help people who were suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.64,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I worked really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.85,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,For decades!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.07,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound impressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.96,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.65,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,People started to call me a Champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.13,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't young anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.82,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It was becoming more difficult \Nfor me to control Ifrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:30.81,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong step, and I could \Nunleash Ifrit by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.46,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought about that, I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:40.49,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I could hurt someone \NI cared about again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:48.64,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So I retired and became an instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,An instructor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.44,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,A teacher at a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.78,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There are schools here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.92,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in a place called \Nthe Kingdom of Ingrassia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.32,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It was a school for kids from other worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.93,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Kids? So there must be quite a few people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,who came here from another world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:13.79,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It was one of them who taught me \Nthat video game line you quoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.46,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not a bad slime!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:24.00,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.60,Flashback,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do today, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:33.23,Flashback,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question. \NWhat should we do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.79,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Those days were so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:46.10,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them eventually went \Noff on their own and left me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:51.61,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But one of them went on \Nto become the Grandmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.08,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:57.20,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible for overseeing \Nall the guilds in every country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.87,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.83,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought there was nothing \Nleft that I could teach anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:10.71,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,And then, possibly because I'm \Nnearing the end of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.90,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,it became more difficult \Nto suppress Ifrit's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.53,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,There was only one thing I could remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.25,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to go on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:29.21,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,My search for the man who summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.63,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.79,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted \Nto find out from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.80,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.74,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,They were such nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.18,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,A little danger-prone, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.57,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.41,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.61,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:09.84,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Slime-san, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I told you, I'm Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.58,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:16.87,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:21.09,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's Satoru. Mikami Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.96,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shizue. Izawa Shizue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:33.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizue-san, you should sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:37.91,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru-san, I'd like to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.60,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.42,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.82,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:58.94,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you ate the curse \Nthat had been cast on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.85,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.80,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I dislike this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.74,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't abhor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.75,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.03,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.80,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be absorbed by this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.36,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,This is... my last request.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:38.37,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you... let me rest inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.43,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the man's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.13,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Leon Cromwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.30,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Leon Cromwell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.87,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,One of the most powerful Demon Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to find out from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:18.95,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted him to acknowledge that I, \Nthis human, had existed... perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:30.28,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,And... if those kids could be saved... \Nand returned to... their world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:37.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to you on the name of \NMikami Satoru... no, Rimuru Tempest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:41.52,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,that I will make certain the Demon Lord \NLeon Cromwell hears your wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.81,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:58.74,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san, my destined one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.98,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.43,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Use unique skill "Predator"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:06.50,sign_17319_145_Use_unique_skill,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1319,1)}Use unique skill "Predator"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.03,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.44,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So that she can dream happy dreams forever \Nand never have to wake from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:30.73,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Please don't \Nleave me behind again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.72,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.24,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.61,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.24,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Shizu is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.39,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about a thing. Rimuru's with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:22.74,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Those potions of his \Nare miracle workers, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.88,Main,Eran,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.69,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.43,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to visit our patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.00,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Are you, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.60,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was just bringing a change \Nof clothes for Lady Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:36.26,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama, may I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.07,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.85,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,That body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:53.74,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's... Rimuru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.91,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:06.20,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,So Shizu passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.17,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Rimuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.00,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.93,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think I wouldn't recognize \Nmy master just because his body changed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.69,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, I didn't mean it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.56,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.50,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,You look a bit like a smaller Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.98,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.25,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.99,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat Shizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.61,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,The way you ate Ifrit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:50.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It was the only burial I could give her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:54.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't consult you, \Nher travel companions, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.42,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:59.76,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,If it's what Shizu wanted, \Nthere was no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.81,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think this was unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.49,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:12.44,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish I could have said goodbye to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.78,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san said she had fun \Ntraveling with you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.84,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Though she also said you \Nwere a bit danger-prone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.01,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you looking at me that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.25,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:27.95,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:31.57,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what about the time you \Ngot caught in that pitfall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.39,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,That was because Eren pushed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.09,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't blame me for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.89,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A spider landed on me out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:42.02,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This suits them a lot better \Nthan being all sad and somber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:42.43,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It was Shizu who took the spider off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.93,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shizu even helped us look \Nfor traps from then on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.56,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shizu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:48.56,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'd say they \Nrelied on her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.56,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}See? It's not just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.02,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still the leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:56.19,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate all your help. \NWe'll be on our way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.37,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Back to your home country?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.25,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we need to report to the Guildmaster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.11,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,about our findings, and about Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.24,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,We won't say anything bad about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.87,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,We'll tell him about you, too, Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.08,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,If anything comes up, \Nyou can always send for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.74,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,There's one last favor we'd like to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:28.35,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take your human form again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:46.11,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Shizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:52.50,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strive to be the kind of leader \Nyou won't have to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:56.29,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,My time adventuring with you \Nwill be my life's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.32,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.48,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,You were like a big sister to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:12.46,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad Shizu-san's last travel \Ncompanions happened to be these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I noticed your \Ngear is looking rather shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.86,Main,Three,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.74,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,It's the scale mail I've always wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.33,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What the heck is this robe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:32.24,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,It's light, but sturdy... and it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:36.58,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do we really deserve such fine equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:40.09,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,It's even lined with Direwolf fur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:43.74,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They're parting gifts. \NOur artisans' best work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:45.06,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,Artisans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.19,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.22,Main,Kaijin,0000,0000,0000,,Our best work? \NThey're actually just prototypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.14,Main,Garm,0000,0000,0000,,How do they feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.31,Main,Dord,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Just speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:04.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce you. From the right, \Nthis is Kaijin, Garm, Myrd, and Dord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.90,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaijin?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.92,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,The blacksmith who's \Nworld-famous for his skills?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.57,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,And Garm, Myrd and Dord...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.74,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,The three Dwarf brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.29,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it my family heirloom! \NThank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.00,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.42,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:26.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Kaijin and his buddies are \Neven more famous than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.55,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They're human national treasures... \Nor is it "dwarven national treasures"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:36.16,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,After raising a fuss big enough \Nto blow their sadness away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.94,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,the three of them left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:42.63,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They're so strong and resilient. \NI should learn from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.93,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who lost everything \Nto the flames so long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:54.15,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,oddly enough, gained the\Npower of fire in her travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:19:00.00,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,She used that power to help the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.63,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,but the flames gradually consumed her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:06.41,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,until, eventually, she could \Nno longer control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.33,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was "Shizue Izawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:15.08,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,She was a Champion whose body housed Ifrit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.63,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,a high-ranked fire spirit, \Nearning her the title "Conqueror of Flames."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.54,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Shizu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:44.13,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Before I can slug the Demon Lord \NLeon Cromwell who made Shizu-san cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:46.09,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I first need to gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:50.82,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man who keeps his promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:57.85,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how the man who thought \Nhe had an ordinary, uneventful life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.93,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and was stabbed on the street and died,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.10,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,was reincarnated in another world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:08.98,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,where he inherited the will of both the Storm Dragon, Veldora, and a human woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.67,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,giving him new purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.34,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,He was a slime by the name of Rimuru,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.45,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and the world was about to usher in
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.92,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,a turbulent, new era, with this \Nlone slime at the center of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.66,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this feels much more right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.10,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you a name and some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.63,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:17.39,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gelmud. You can think \Nof me as your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:22.75,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:31.27,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a name... and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.45,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Geld.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.64,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Geld...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:46.86,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you will take possession \Nof the Great Forest of Jura
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:49.63,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,and become the Orc Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.66,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Attack of the Ogres."
